author: #s#8059
description: Commands to gain insights into your server's population. Get a quick overview on how many members each of server's roles have, or see stats about how long members have been on your server.
install_msg: Hello, thanks for installing this cog! The commands in here are some of the first I made back in 2018. If you have any suggestions in terms of stat commands, feel free to let me know!
short: Commands to gain insights into your server's population.
name: MemberStats
